title: Karishma Kali Kaa
subTitle: A devout young woman is falsely accused of murdering a priest and absconding with the temple jewels. With her fate hanging in the balance, the woman seeks divine intervention to prove her innocence.

title: Kartoos
subTitle: ACP Jay Suryavanshi assigns an inmate on death row, Jeet, the task of killing Jagat, a terrorist. Things take a turn when Jeet falls in love with Mini and gets distracted from his mission.

title: Masoom
subTitle: D K Malhotra leads a peaceful life with his wife and two daughters. But all of this changes when he is forced to bring a boy, who is his son from a previous relationship, home after his mother dies.

title: Bal Hanuman Return Of The Demon
subTitle: Bal Hanuman and his friends join together to defeat the crocodile demon who has been brought to life in order to create havoc on Earth.

title: Hello Brother
subTitle: In a heated confrontation, Hero is shot dead and his heart is transplanted into Inspector Vishal. As a bizarre consequence, Hero's ghost haunts Vishal, demanding revenge for his murder.

title: Dilwale
subTitle: Despite the family rivalry, Raj and Meera fall in love other but a misunderstanding causes them to part ways. Years later, fate brings them together when their siblings fall for each other.

title: Gabbar Is Back
subTitle: The city's administration wrongs Aditya, a commoner. To avenge his tragedy, he disguises himself as a vigilante, Gabbar, and teams up with honest government officers to expose the corrupt.

title: Dil Hai Tumhaara
subTitle: Sarita raises Shalu, her spouse's love child, and her daughter, Nimmi, but she does not forgive Shalu's past. When she discovers that Shalu is growing close to Nimmi's lover, things become worse.

title: Sholay
subTitle: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

title: Apmaan Ki Aag
subTitle: While celebrating his girlfriend Mona's birthday, Vikrant gets humiliated by two goons. He vows to exact revenge but it takes him down a difficult and thorny path.

title: Apmaan Ki Aag
subTitle: While celebrating his girlfriend Mona's birthday, Vikrant gets humiliated by two goons. He vows to exact revenge but it takes him down a difficult and thorny path.

title: Tejaa
subTitle: Tejaa's family gets murdered when he is a child. Later, in an attempt to seek revenge, he traces down the three goons who were responsible.

title: Ram Aur Shyam
subTitle: Ram escapes from his home when he learns that his abusive brother-in-law plans to kill him. Justice is meted out when Shyam, Ram's long-lost twin, accidentally takes his place.

title: Hathyar
subTitle: Circumstances force Rohit, an innocent man, to follow his father's footsteps and enter the world of crime. However, things take a dangerous turn when the politicians view him as a threat.

title: Prem Ratan Dhan Payo
subTitle: Prem, who looks like Prince Yuvraj Vijay Singh, replaces him just before Vijay is to be crowned king. Although Vijay is engaged to Princess Maithili, she falls in love with Prem.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Chote Sarkar
subTitle: When two cops frame Amar, a businessman, of murdering his uncle, he pretends to be of unsound mind to escape apprehension and find the real murderer.

title: Jeet
subTitle: Karan, a gangster, falls in love with Kajal, but she marries Raju because of her father's poor health. Later, when Raju finds out about his father's illegal business, Karan is hired to kill him.

title: Andolan
subTitle: Adarsh and Aniket are two brothers who study in the same college. However, when they graduate and plan to establish a career, both of them choose different paths and gradually drift apart.

title: Andolan
subTitle: Adarsh and Aniket are two brothers who study in the same college. However, when they graduate and plan to establish a career, both of them choose different paths and gradually drift apart.

title: Qaidi
subTitle: Ravi Verma, a CBI officer, infiltrates the gang of a notorious criminal, Kali, pretending to be him. However, things take a turn when Kali regains his consciousness.

title: Prahaar
subTitle: Major Pratap meets Peter during his training days in the Indian Army. However, when he is openly killed by thugs and no one seeks justice for him, Major Pratap takes matters into his own hands.

title: Dillagi
subTitle: Ranvir and Rajvir, two inseparable brothers, support each other through thick and thin. However, they find themselves in a dilemma when both of them fall in love with the same woman.

title: Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam
subTitle: A newly-wed man discovers that his wife is in love with another man and decides to unite them. Ignoring the ridicule he might have to face for this, he takes his wife to Italy in search of her love.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Hum Tumhare Hain Sanam
subTitle: Gopal is happily married to Radha until she meets her friend Suraj and starts obsessing over his singing career. Gopal suspects that they are secretly seeing each other and decides to leave her.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.
